name: The I Ching of Computing
description:
A collection of 54 progressive terms focused on IT and computing.

If you dream of kicking Google and SAP from their thrones, you better own this powerful tool for generating thousands of unheard-of technology concepts!

The I Ching introduces coincidence into the Matrix. So, choose an innovative-sounding buzzword, fax it to your shareholders, and let coders in India figure out the rest while you browse your next yacht on Alibaba.

resolution: 5600×5600
